des:
Easily control your smart home devices with Amazon Alexa.

Amazon Alexa and iMagic smart home devices work together to help you control home appliance easily and efficiently. 

You can simply ask Amazon Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light. There is no need to go to the switch to adjust your home light, just talk to Amazon Alexa.

After connecting Amazon Alexa to your iMagic smart home devices in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our "iMagic Living" app in google play store or apple App Store;
(2) Register one iMagic account in our "iMagic Living" app;
(3) You need to have some iMagic smart home devices in hand;
(4) Pair these devices in our "iMagic Living" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "iMagic Living" skill;
(5) Download Amazon Alexa app from google play store or apple App Store;
(6) Search "iMagic Living" skill from the Amazon Alexa app skill category;
(7) Click enable skill of "iMagic Living", and you will be navigated to iMagic login page;
(8) Input your iMagic account username and password, you will be redirected the success page;
(9) Now all setup is finished;

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
"Alexa, discover my devices."
"Alexa, turn on the bedroom light."
"Alexa, turn off the bedroom light."
......

If you have any problems when you use this skill, you can contact us with email: imagic@greatstartools.com.
